name: GitHub for My Work Projects
tagline: Projects I have worked on that proved useful outside of work
body:
### Work projects GitHub
This Git will expand when I get new projects, mostly java, but I'll be learning some different stuff here and there and making applications for people to use. Fork my project and try your hand at improving and using my stuff.

##Current Projects
These are the current projects I'm working on
###Zip String Replacer
This is a replacer that opens up a zip folder replaces a string with another, and then repackages the entire thing. It's helpful if you have a zip up in AWS and need to replace a url in a couple of documents for a zip package.

##Dropped Projects
###Py Video Converter
Using the ffmpeg library, I made a short program that converts videos into mp4 format.
